  "signal_description": "Count the number of late deliveries based on the time difference between the actual delivery date and the scheduled finish date. The query is performed on the 'defaultview-183' table. The 'Late deliveries' column is calculated by subtracting the 'Scheduled Finish Date' from the 'Actual Delivery Date'. If the time difference is greater than 0 seconds and less than or equal to 1 day, it is categorized as '0-1 days'. If the time difference is greater than 1 day and less than or equal to 2 days, it is categorized as 'b) 1-2 days', and so on. If the time difference is greater than 9 days and less than or equal to 10 days, it is categorized as 'j) 9-10 days'. Any time difference greater than 10 days is categorized as 'k) >10 days'. The results are ordered in ascending order based on the 'Time difference' column."
}
